# Review gates for the shared coordination repo (one repo, many projects).
# A merge is the human-in-the-loop handoff approval, enforced by branch protection
# (require review from Code Owners on the protected `main` branch).
#
# Scope review PER PROJECT: each project's teams own their own folder. Contract changes
# are a cross-team commitment, so list BOTH teams for that project. Copy this block per
# project you add.

/projects/example-app/contracts/   @acme/example-fe @acme/example-be
/projects/example-app/decisions/   @acme/example-fe @acme/example-be
/projects/example-app/handoffs/    @acme/example-fe @acme/example-be

# Add the next project the same way:
# /projects/<project>/contracts/   @acme/<project>-fe @acme/<project>-be
# /projects/<project>/handoffs/    @acme/<project>-fe @acme/<project>-be

# Shared schema / tooling / CI: platform owners.
/_schema/      @acme/platform-team
/_template.md  @acme/platform-team
/tools/        @acme/platform-team
/.github/      @acme/platform-team
